{
  "openapi": "3.0.0",
  "info": {
    "title": "SmailproAPI Documentation",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "description": "\n## Quick Start\n\n### Prerequisites\nBefore using this API, you need to:\n\n1. **Create an account** at [my.sonjj.com](https://my.sonjj.com) to obtain your API key\n2. **Purchase credits** by following our guide: [SonjJ API Credits System Guide](https://sonjj.com/sonjj-api-credits-system-guide/)\n\n### Authentication\nAll API requests require authentication using an API key. Include your API key in the request header:\n\n```\nX-Api-Key: your_api_key_here\n```\n\n\n\nSmailpro API provides temporary Gmail addresses for receiving OTP messages, account registrations, newsletter subscriptions, and more. It allows users to generate and manage temporary Gmail inboxes without registering a real account."
  },
